Package hash.int64

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LongHasher
    A 64-bit hash function.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DegskiLongHasher
    Based on https://gist.github.com/degski/6e2069d6035ae04d5d6f64981c995ec2.
    IdentityLongHasher
    Implements identity hash function.
    Murmur3LongHasher
    Implements Murmur3 64-bit finalizer (https://github.com/aappleby/smhasher/wiki/MurmurHash3)
    PhiLongHasher
    Multiply by the golden ratio and mix high bits into low bits.
    Variant13LongHasher
    Variant 13 of Murmur3 64-bit finalizer (http://zimbry.blogspot.com/2011/09/better-bit-mixing-improving-on.html)
    WangLongHasher
    Based on https://naml.us/post/inverse-of-a-hash-function/.
